casebody.data:
No. 105,

Orig.

Kansas v. Colorado. [For earlier order herein, see, e. g., 526 U. S. 1048.]

Motion of the Special Master for fees and reimbursement of expenses granted, and the Special Master is awarded a total of $112,783.95 for the period March 3, 1999, through January 28, 2000, to be paid equally by the parties.
